snippet.title: Infernales First Teaser
snippet.description:
Infernales - infernal, fleshy, bloodthirsty, killer first-person shooter, in which you, because of a wild bureaucratic error, were sent to hell, instead of paradise. But you do not agree with this, and you are ready to shoot all the creatures of hell to fix it.
Several weapons, hundreds of monsters, hard rock and an infernal atmosphere ...
In development.
Recorded in the engine.
